===Etymology===
{{OE.}} ''upbreiden''; {{AS.}} ''upp'' up + ''bregdan'' to draw, twist, weave, or the kindred; {{Icel.}} ''bregða'' to draw, brandish, braid, deviate from, change, break off, upbraid. See [[up]], and [[braid]] ''(transitive)''.

